title: Cosplay Guest Judges Announced
content:
JAFAX is pleased to announce three guest judges this year for the Cosplay Crafting Competition!

Caitlin Bannister (C80s Thingamabobs), Ashlee Kalthoff (Disfusional Studios), and Rachel Crouch (Spindrift Cosplay) are all talented cosplayers in their own right, and now will use their sense of crafting and artistic experience to judge this year's Cosplay Crafting entrants!
